1
00:00:00,990 --> 00:00:05,156
My name is Samer Elias Saeed, born in Mosul in 1974

2
00:00:05,703 --> 00:00:08,542
I work as a Syriac language teacher

3
00:00:08,880 --> 00:00:13,568
At Christian community schools in Mosul

4
00:00:13,593 --> 00:00:16,224
The Tahdhib School and the Tahira School

5
00:00:16,249 --> 00:00:17,734
And Maouna School

6
00:00:17,759 --> 00:00:19,323
And Shamoun Safa School

7
00:00:19,348 --> 00:00:21,536
And Ghassaniya School

8
00:00:22,474 --> 00:00:27,578
As for my work in Mosul, I documented the churches and their history

9
00:00:28,021 --> 00:00:33,880
I specialized in researching the history of how the churches were founded

10
00:00:33,905 --> 00:00:37,942
I have many articles about these churches

11
00:00:37,967 --> 00:00:41,692
And about the rituals and celebrations held there

12
00:00:41,717 --> 00:00:46,107
In addition, I archived Christian heritage and history in Mosul

13
00:00:46,132 --> 00:00:50,039
From 2008 up to the present

14
00:00:50,535 --> 00:00:56,967
Regarding the Armenian Orthodox Church, I documented it in articles

15
00:00:56,993 --> 00:01:01,914
Especially about the rituals and celebrations that were held

16
00:01:01,939 --> 00:01:05,509
I also covered the celebrations that took place for Christmas

17
00:01:05,665 --> 00:01:08,764
Which differ from the other Christian denominations

18
00:01:08,789 --> 00:01:13,477
Which usually occurred on December 25 each year

19
00:01:13,579 --> 00:01:17,592
Except the Armenian Orthodox Church, which celebrated it on January 6

20
00:01:17,800 --> 00:01:21,108
Unlike the other Christian denominations
